        <Parent_String>Sub-Saharan African Middle Stone Age periods [300015678], prehistoric Sub-Saharan African periods [300015667], prehistoric African [300015649], African (general, continental cultures) [300015647], styles, periods, and cultures by region [300111079], Styles and Periods (hierarchy name) [300015646], Styles and Periods Facet [300264088]</Parent_String>
